#What is Ajax

Asynchronous Javascript & XML
Set of Web Technologies
Send & Receive data asynchronously
Doest interfere with current web page
JSON has replace XML for the most part


#XmlHttpRequest (XHR) Object

API in the form of an ObjectProvided by browser's JS environment
Method transfer data between client/server
Can be used with other protocols than XmlHttpRequestCan work with data other than XML  (JSON, plain text)

